in two weeks, Vicky.

800
00:45:27,726 --> 00:45:29,518
- Yeah, I know.
- Okay?

801
00:45:29,603 --> 00:45:30,895
I know, you're right.

802
00:45:30,979 --> 00:45:33,105
Cristina loves you.

803
00:45:33,189 --> 00:45:34,732
I would never...

804
00:45:34,816 --> 00:45:37,735
Yes, yes, and Cristina and I
are a good fit.

805
00:45:37,819 --> 00:45:39,653
