00:47:35,937 --> 00:47:36,937
You had a good time?

835
00:47:37,022 --> 00:47:39,565
Yeah, Seville is breathtaking.

836
00:47:39,649 --> 00:47:40,983
We ran into some friends
from New York.

837
00:47:41,067 --> 00:47:43,402
Had a chance to spend some time
with them, which was great.

838
00:47:43,486 --> 00:47:44,570
A little too much time.

