863
00:49:06,528 --> 00:49:08,737
Yes. I don't...
Yes, I think so. I don't know.

864
00:49:08,822 --> 00:49:09,863
I have to go.

865
00:49:09,948 --> 00:49:11,031
Where are you going?

866
00:49:11,116 --> 00:49:12,991
