867
00:49:13,076 --> 00:49:15,077
I'm going to the hospital.

868
00:49:15,161 --> 00:49:17,204
Should I come with you?

869
00:49:18,206 --> 00:49:20,415
No, no, I don't think that
would be a good idea for her.

870
00:49:20,500 --> 00:49:22,709
- She's a mess.
- Well, all right.

871
00:49:22,794 --> 00:49:25,796
- Call me if you want me to come, okay?
- Okay, of course.

872
00:49:25,880 --> 00:49:27,089
Of course.

873
00:49:28,091 --> 00:49:30,926
Juan Antonio hurried out
in the dead of night.

874
00:49:35,723 --> 00:49:39,852
Cristina tried to go back to sleep,
but had an uneasy feeling.

875
00:49:39,936 --> 00:49:44,106
She dozed restively,
but awoke at the darkest hour.

876
00:49:51,948 --> 00:49:53,323
