904
00:51:29,837 --> 00:51:30,879
She has to stay with us.

905
00:51:30,964 --> 00:51:34,049
I mean, she has no money,
she has no one capable of caring for her...

906
00:51:35,969 --> 00:51:38,220
I mean, I-I always...

907
00:51:39,389 --> 00:51:42,849
I was always her connection
to the real life.

908
00:51:42,934 --> 00:51:47,187
Uh-huh, I understand, but I mean,
how can she stay here?

909
00:51:47,272 --> 00:51:49,314
You know, I think...

910
00:51:49,399 --> 00:51:52,734
I think that she can't be trusted
to stay alone, that's the problem.

911
00:51:52,819 --> 00:51:55,487
Because, I mean, even if...
let me think...

912
00:51:55,571 --> 00:51:59,866
even if I... if a place
could be worked out...

913
00:51:59,951 --> 00:52:01,994
Well, maybe she needs
psychiatric help.

914
00:52:02,078 --> 00:52:04,663
No, she's always had
bad experiences with doctors.

915
00:52:04,747 --> 00:52:07,666
I understand,
but where is she gonna stay?

916
00:52:07,750 --> 00:52:08,959
In there.

917
00:52:11,004 --> 00:52:13,046
How long is she gonna stay here?

918
00:52:14,090 --> 00:52:15,799
Cristina, I know...

919
00:52:17,343 --> 00:52:19,720
- this is not what you had in mind.
- No... I understand.

920
00:52:19,804 --> 00:52:21,847
