924
00:52:27,729 --> 00:52:29,980
Listen, I've been through this
with her before.

925
00:52:31,274 --> 00:52:33,692
So... I mean if...

926
00:52:33,776 --> 00:52:35,027
Shit.

927
00:52:35,111 --> 00:52:37,529
(curses in Spanish)

928
00:52:37,613 --> 00:52:40,532
