1513
01:26:41,530 --> 01:26:42,530
Yeah?

1514
01:26:44,533 --> 01:26:48,703
He wants me to have a good-bye lunch
with him tomorrow at noon.

1515
01:26:48,788 --> 01:26:49,788
Oh, that's perfect.

